comment: /**  * Resets and returns elapsed time in milliseconds.  */
code: /**  * Resets and returns elapsed time in milliseconds.  */ public long reset() {     long nowNS = System.nanoTime().     try {         return TimeValue.nsecToMSec(nowNS - startNS).     } finally {         startNS = nowNS.     } }

comment: /**  * Resets and logs elapsed time in milliseconds.  */
code: /**  * Resets and logs elapsed time in milliseconds.  */ public void resetAndLog(String label) {     logger.fine(label + ": " + reset() + "ms"). }
